OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering footballer
OL,4,Cafter driving van into crowd
OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of murder
OL,7,Fafter driving a van into a crowd of
OL,8,Fpeople on a Christmas night out and
OL,9,Fkilling one.
OL,11,FA jury took 20 hours of deliberating
OL,12,Fto convict Zac Newman guilty by a
OL,13,Fmajority of 10 to two of causing the
OL,14,Fdeath of Sam Wilson.
OL,16,FWilson, 26, died after Newman
OL,17,Fdeliberately drove into the group of
OL,18,Fpeople in Ilkeston market place during
OL,19,Fthe early hours of December 16 last
OL,20,Fyear.
