OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering footballer
OL,4,Cafter driving van into crowd
OL,6,FWilson, who was a talented Derbyshire
OL,7,Ffootballer, suffered "catastrophic"
OL,8,Finjuries following the collision.
OL,10,FTwo other people suffered non-fatal
OL,11,Finjuries and despite attempts to save
OL,12,FMr Wilson, he died at the site of the
OL,13,Fcollision just after 2am.
OL,15,FNewman, of The Crescent, Stapleford,
OL,16,FNottinghamshire, was found guilty of
OL,17,Fmurder, one count of wounding with
OL,18,Fintent and one count of attempted
OL,19,Fwounding with intent at Derby Crown
OL,20,FCourt.
