OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Matt Croome,
OL,7,Fof East Midlands Special Operations
OL,8,FUnit, said: "Zac Newman used a van as
OL,9,Fa weapon, and in a drug-fuelled rage
OL,10,Fdrove into a crowd of people who were
OL,11,Fjust stood gathered after enjoying a
OL,12,Fnight out in Ilkeston.
OL,14,F"His completely reckless and
OL,15,Firresponsible actions that night has
OL,16,Fled to heart-breaking devastation for
OL,17,FSam's family, and our thoughts remain
OL,18,Fwith them at this time."
