OL,6,FDerbyshire Police said Newman, 27, had
OL,7,Fbeen drinking and taking cocaine just
OL,8,Fhours before, and then did not stop
OL,9,Fafter the collision but drove back
OL,10,Fhome where he was arrested by officers.
OL,12,FThe defendant, of The Crescent,
OL,13,FStapleford, Nottingham, had denied
OL,14,Fmurdering Mr Wilson, of Long Eaton,
OL,15,Fand seriously injuring the two other
OL,16,Fmen.
