OL,4,Cafter driving van into crowd
OL,6,FJudge Shaun Smith KC adjourned the
OL,7,Fsentencing saying: "It is a life
OL,8,Fsentence but it is a case of the
OL,9,Ftariff (how many years it will be
OL,10,Funtil Newman is eligible to apply for
OL,11,Fparole)."
OL,13,FAfter the verdicts were delivered,
OL,14,FNewman admitted the killing put him in
OL,15,Fbreach of a suspended sentence,
OL,16,Fimposed at Nottingham Crown Court in
OL,17,FMarch 2022, for dealing drugs.
