OL,6,FOn the first day of the trial, more
OL,7,Fthan two weeks ago, relatives of Mr
OL,8,FWilson, who was a member of the Curzon
OL,9,FFootball Club and also a Derby County
OL,10,Fseason ticket holder, wept openly as
OL,11,FCCTV footage was shown during the
OL,12,Fopening remarks by prosecutor John
OL,13,FLloyd Jones KC.
OL,15,FMr Lloyd-Jones said that Newman had
OL,16,F"made up his mind" to get into his van
OL,17,Fand "continue the violent
OL,18,Fconfrontation he had started"
OL,19,Ffollowing an afternoon of drinking and
OL,20,Fgradually getting angrier in a series
OL,21,Fof pubs.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
