OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering footballer
OL,4,Cafter driving van into crowd
OL,6,F"He drove from the car park in
OL,7,FPimlico, mounted the corner and headed
OL,8,Ftowards the Market Inn", Mr Lloyd-
OL,9,FJones told the court.
OL,11,F"He drove directly towards the group
OL,12,Fof people, at not more than nine to
OL,13,F10mph. He had ample opportunity to
OL,14,Favoid them and ample opportunity to
OL,15,Fstop the van but he chose not to,
OL,16,Falthough he braked slightly and then
OL,17,Fdrove on. People were knocked over."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/17
