OL,6,FEarlier, Mr Lloyd-Jones told the court
OL,7,Fthat Newman had finished work at about
OL,8,F1.30pm ahead of Christmas and headed
OL,9,Fto the Half Moon, at Burton Road, in
OL,10,FLittleover, where he had a couple of
OL,11,Fpints.
OL,13,FHe left there and went to the Man of
OL,14,FIron pub in Stapleford for a couple of
OL,15,Fhours where he had three pints of
OL,16,Fbeer, two vodkas and two shots, before
OL,17,Fheading home to get changed and go out
OL,18,Fagain to the Midland Hotel where he
OL,19,Fstayed from 6.30pm to 8.30pm.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/17
