OL,6,FNewman then headed into Ilkeston town
OL,7,Fcentre, parked his white van in the
OL,8,FPimlico car park and headed for The
OL,9,FHarrow pub before moving on to the
OL,10,FMarket Inn at about 10.40pm.
OL,12,FBetween then and 2am, Mr Lloyd-Jones
OL,13,Fsaid that Newman drank "five doubles,
OL,14,Ftwo shots and snorted cocaine on five
OL,15,Foccasions".
