OL,6,FMr Lloyd-Jones also said that
OL,7,Fwitnesses had stated that Newman was
OL,8,Fangry and on one occasion around
OL,9,Fmidnight confronted customer Harry
OL,10,FQuinn in the toilets and later slapped
OL,11,Fhim in the face with his left hand
OL,12,Fwhen Mr Quinn tackled him about the
OL,13,Finitial confrontation.
OL,15,FNewman also became increasingly
OL,16,Fagitated after a girl he knew, and who
OL,17,Fhe was "chatting to and flirting with"
OL,18,Fand who he tried to kiss, was paid
OL,19,Fattention by another male called Quinn
OL,20,FRaeside.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/17
