OL,6,FDoor staff reacted and ushered Mr
OL,7,FRaeside towards the entrance.
OL,9,FMr Lloyd-Jones said: "It should have
OL,10,Fbeen all over at this point but Newman
OL,11,Fdecided to follow Quinn Raeside and
OL,12,Ffinding him in the foyer, provoked
OL,13,Fanother confrontation.
OL,15,FThey both exited the Market Inn and
OL,16,Fcongregated in groups outside in the
OL,17,FMarket Place.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/17
