OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering footballer
OL,4,Cafter driving van into crowd
OL,6,F"It should still have been an end to
OL,7,Fit but Newman sought out Mr Raeside
OL,8,Fand punched him in the face and he was
OL,9,Falso knocked to the floor. A fight
OL,10,Fensued and another bystander was
OL,11,Fpunched who tried to calm the
OL,12,Fsituation down."
OL,14,FMr Lloyd-Jones said Newman was
OL,15,Fescorted out of the Market Place by
OL,16,Fthree people and he headed to his van,
OL,17,Fwhich he said he "deliberately drove
OL,18,Fto the Market Place" and "headed
OL,19,Fdirectly into the group".
