OL,6,FBut Mr Lloyd-Jones said Mr Wilson was
OL,7,Fknocked down, Newman drove over him
OL,8,Fand dragged him along the Market Place
OL,9,Funder the vehicle, as he gathered
OL,10,Fspeed, depositing him at the top of
OL,11,FSouth Street.
OL,13,FParamedics attended and did all they
OL,14,Fcould to save him but Mr Wilson was
OL,15,Fpronounced dead at the scene.
OL,17,FHe suffered multiple injuries but the
OL,18,Fcause of death was trauma to the chest
OL,19,Fwhich fractured his rib cage and
OL,20,Fcaused his lungs to collapse.
