OL,6,FMr Lloyd-Jones said that Newman drove
OL,7,Fhome, where he was arrested shortly
OL,8,Fafterwards by police officers.
OL,10,FHe was interviewed five times without
OL,11,Fmaking any comment and then finally
OL,12,Fmade a statement admitting that he
OL,13,Fdrove the vehicle but that he was
OL,14,Funaware he had struck anyone and had
OL,15,Fno intention of killing or wounding
OL,16,Fanyone.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G15/17
